data.description: Welcome to the epitome of charm in Collinsville, IL! This delightful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick ranch home is a perfect blend of comfort and style. Enjoy the warmth of two wood-burning fireplaces, creating a cozy atmosphere in the main living spaces. The finished walkout basement with a bar is an entertainer's dream, perfect for hosting gatherings. Step outside to a spacious yard, offering endless possibilities for outdoor activities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this adorable home yours – schedule a showing today and envision a future filled with warmth and cherished memories. Welcome to your dream home in Collinsville! Buyer or buyer's agent to verify MLS details.
